<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_260_line_1576664661551_7969">L </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l5"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft ʒu
                            <expan>VVermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l6">vıcʒtum in Nıder payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_260_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum . als Jr vns von <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> vnd ~ des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l8"><expan>Truchſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> habt für eẅch gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l9">Strawbıng auf den ertag ʒu nacht nach dem ſunntag <expan>Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l10">in der <expan>vaſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt etc Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd als Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l11"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratg<ex>eſellen</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hall<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>volkm<ex>eir</ex></expan> . vormalʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l12"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd ſıe <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in ırem <expan>lecʒ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l13"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſıe geraten deẅcht daʒ Jr <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l14"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt für eẅch <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> hett . ſo <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l15"><expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch für eẅch darcʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / alſda ʒu <expan>berede<ex>n</ex></expan> wıe es von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l16">einr kerung vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> artıkel <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> beſteen ſölt / Alſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l17">gen den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> vnd ~ dem <expan>Truchſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l18">den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag . den Jr vns für eẅch gen Strawbıng <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l19"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> von den <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒu reden als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l20">eẅch denn vor <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . alſo wer auf beıd ſeyten auf dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l21">ʒeıt darcʒu reıten werd / daʒ <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> acht tag dauor vnd acht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l22">tag darnach <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> ſıcher ſein <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>VV<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber daʒ vns ın der ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l23">ſölıch ſach <expan>anſtıeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır ʒu dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> tag für eẅch niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l24"><expan>geſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan> Das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vor <expan>verkünd<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l25"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>deſgleıch<ex>en</ex></expan> getrawten wır eẅch auch wol . Denn wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_260_r1l26">wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> ſtolaſtıce </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_260" id="130r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft zu <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, vicztum in
            Niderpayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns von <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom
                <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> und des <expan>Truchsess<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag
                <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan> habt für ewch gen Strawbing auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">ertag zu nacht nach dem sunntag
                      <expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan></q>17.03.1416</note>
</app> in der <expan>vast<ex>en</ex></expan> schierist etc., das
              <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und als ir
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>ratg<ex>esellen</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hall<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Volkm<ex>eir</ex></expan> vormalz <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch
                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sie <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in irem <expan>lecz<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief
                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie geraten dewcht, daz ir
              <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt für ewch <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan> hett,
            so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch für ewch darczu <expan>schik<ex>en,</ex></expan>
            als da zu <expan>berede<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie es von einr kerung und
                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> artikel <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> besteen sölt.
            Also <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir gen den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> und dem
                <expan>Truchsess<ex>en</ex></expan> auf den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag,
            den ir uns für ewch gen Strawbing <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan> habt,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en,</ex></expan> von den <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dazu reden, als
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd ewch denn vor
              <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also wer auf beid seyten auf die zeit darczu reiten werd,
            daz <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> acht tag davor und acht tag darnach
                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> sicher sein <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber, daz uns in der zeit sölich sach
                <expan>anstiess<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir zu dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
            tag für ewch niht <expan>geschik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möcht<ex>en,</ex></expan> das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vor <expan>verkünd<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>desgleich<ex>en</ex></expan> getrawten wir ewch auch wol. Denn wo wir
                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi> stolastice. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
